## 四、初始化项目

### 4.1 创建 Conda 环境

在项目根目录执行：

```powershell
conda create -n sdn python=3.11
conda activate sdn
```

---

### 4.2 安装采集端依赖

```powershell
pip install -r collector\requirements.txt
```

---

### 4.3 安装后端依赖

```powershell
pip install -r backend\requirements.txt
```

---

### 4.4 安装前端依赖

```powershell
cd frontend
npm install
cd ..
```

---

### 4.5 安装 PySpark 分析依赖

```powershell
cd analysis
pip install -r requirements.txt
cd ..
```

---

### 4.6 安装机器学习模块依赖

```powershell
cd ml
pip install -r requirements.txt
cd ..
```

