## 七、导入外部开源历史数据

外部数据来源：

```text
https://github.com/v5tech/weibo-trending-hot-search
```

建议先导入一个月数据进行测试，不要一开始直接导入全部数据。

---

### 7.1 测试导入一个月数据

在项目根目录执行：

```powershell
python tools/import_v5tech_weibo_dataset.py `
  --dataset-dir external/v5tech-weibo-trending-hot-search `
  --start-date 2021-11-08 `
  --end-date 2021-11-30
```

---

### 7.2 检查外部历史数据表

进入 MySQL 后执行：

```sql
USE weibo_hot;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_count
FROM hot_search_v5tech_history;

SELECT dataset_date, COUNT(*) AS cnt, MAX(hot_value) AS max_hot
FROM hot_search_v5tech_history
GROUP BY dataset_date
ORDER BY dataset_date DESC
LIMIT 10;
```

---

### 7.3 同步导入到 hot_search_raw 表

如果需要让现有页面、PySpark 分析、机器学习爆发趋势识别、情感分析和主题聚类直接使用外部历史数据，可以加上 `--sync-raw` 参数。

```powershell
python tools/import_v5tech_weibo_dataset.py `
  --dataset-dir external/v5tech-weibo-trending-hot-search `
  --start-date 2021-11-08 `
  --end-date 2021-11-30 `
  --sync-raw
```

---

### 7.4 检查同步结果

```sql
USE weibo_hot;

SELECT source, COUNT(*) AS total_count
FROM hot_search_raw
GROUP BY source;

SELECT title, rank_num, hot_value, source, fetch_time
FROM hot_search_raw
WHERE source = 'v5tech_dataset'
ORDER BY fetch_time DESC, rank_num ASC
LIMIT 20;
```

---

### 7.5 清理错误导入的数据

清理外部历史表：

```sql
DELETE FROM hot_search_v5tech_history
WHERE source = 'v5tech_dataset'
  AND dataset_date BETWEEN '2021-11-08' AND '2021-11-30';
```

清理同步到 `hot_search_raw` 的数据：

```sql
DELETE FROM hot_search_raw
WHERE source = 'v5tech_dataset'
  AND DATE(fetch_time) BETWEEN '2021-11-08' AND '2021-11-30';
```

---

### 7.6 自动清理后重新导入

```powershell
python tools/import_v5tech_weibo_dataset.py `
  --dataset-dir external/v5tech-weibo-trending-hot-search `
  --start-date 2021-11-08 `
  --end-date 2021-11-30 `
  --sync-raw `
  --clear-range
```

---

### 7.7 导入 2024 年数据

测试没有问题后，可以导入 2024 年全年数据：

```powershell
python tools/import_v5tech_weibo_dataset.py `
  --dataset-dir external/v5tech-weibo-trending-hot-search `
  --start-date 2024-01-01 `
  --end-date 2024-12-31 `
